This directory contains images for the EasyConfigs documentation and README.

## Required Images:

### Logo & Branding
- `logo.png` - Main EasyConfigs logo for README header
- `mie-avatar.png` - Creator avatar/profile image

### Feature Screenshots
- `config-interface.png` - Visual configuration interface screenshot
- `responsive.png` - Responsive design showcase across devices

### How It Works Screenshots
