## Image Guidelines:
- Use PNG format for screenshots with transparency
- Optimize images for web (keep under 500KB when possible)
- Use consistent styling and color scheme
- Include dark/light mode versions if applicable
- Resolution: 1200x800 or higher for main screenshots
